(-------------------------------------) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Search automatically and store results in the database) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py search-auto --title "frontend developer" --keywords) Tj
T* (    "react,javascript" --country US --remote) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Another automatic search example) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py search-auto --title "python developer" --keywords) Tj
T* (    "django,backend,remote" --remote) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Search and filter results using the current filtered workflow) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py search-filtered --title "frontend developer" --keywords) Tj
T* (    "react,javascript" --country US --remote) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Comment:) Tj
T* (search-auto stores results in the database. After running it, check with stats and queue.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (APPROVE OR REVIEW CONTACTS) Tj
T* (--------------------------) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Approve the newest review contacts) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py approve-recent-contacts --limit 20 --recent-hours 24) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Archive sent contacts) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py archive-contacts --sent) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Restore all archived contacts) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py unarchive-contacts --all) Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Comment:) Tj
T* (These are useful after extraction, once you start managing sendable contacts.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (VERIFICATION EMAIL WORKFLOW) Tj
T* (---------------------------) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Send a verification email to one contact) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py send-verification-email --email person@example.com --name "Jane) Tj
T* (    Doe") Tj
T* () Tj
T* () Tj
T* (    # Preview the verification email without saving or sending) Tj
T* (    python3 devnavigator.py send-verification-email --email person@example.com --name "Jane) Tj
ET
endstream
